# The app is taken from https://github.com/Oreste-Luci/netflix-oss-example

# The following modifications were done in order to be able to use the system into the attack graph generator.

1. In the Dockerfiles the ADD command is changed.
2. The rabbitmq is now locally build. It is the same one. The Dockerfile is taken from https://github.com/docker-library/rabbitmq/tree/5bdfc8547e813bbe2e0ef725738252792780d744
3. The docker-compose file is put in the root of the project.
4. Legacy flag links has been deleted. New one "networks has been added" and extended to correspond the image.
5. Additional ports have been deleted in order to correspond to the image.
